y Play for 6 months to 7 years!\n\nChildren will have the opportunity to explore a variety of sensory and messy play stations designed to encourage creativity, imagination, learning, and play. Our sessions are child-led, allowing little ones to explore at their own pace in a safe and welcoming environment.\n\nPlay, explore, create, and get messy!"},{"marketVariantId":"Indonesian","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"INDONESIAN","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Indonesian","commentText":"Petualangan bermain kotor yang menyenangkan di Rivervmill Bersejarah dengan Program Bermain Liburan Sekolah kami untuk anak usia 6 bulan hingga 7 tahun!\n\nAnak-anak akan memiliki kesempatan untuk menjelajahi berbagai stasiun bermain sensorik dan kotor yang dirancang untuk mendorong kreativitas, imajinasi, pembelajaran, dan bermain. Sesi kami dipimpin oleh anak-anak, memungkinkan si kecil untuk menjelajahi dengan kecepatan mereka sendiri dalam lingkungan yang aman dan ramah.\n\nBermain, menjelajahi, berkreasi, dan bermain kotor!"},{"marketVariantId":"Korean","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"KOREAN","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Korean","commentText":"역사적인 리버밀에서 펼쳐지는 신나는 오감놀이 모험! 6개월부터 7세까지 아이들을 위한 특별 방학 놀이 프로그램입니다.\n\n아이들은 창의력 상상력 학습 그리고 놀이를 장려하도록 설계된 다양한 감각 및 오감놀이 공간을 마음껏 탐색할 수 있습니다. 아이들이 주도적으로 참여하는 방식으로 진행되어 안전하고 편안한 환경에서 아이들이 자신의 속도에 맞춰 자유롭게 탐색할 수 있습니다.\n\n놀고 탐색하고 만들고 마음껏 오감놀이를 즐겨보세요!"},{"marketVariantId":"French","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"FRENCH","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"French","commentText":"Vivez une aventure sensorielle et ludique inoubliable au Moulin Historique de Rivermill avec nos activités pendant les vacances scolaires pour les enfants de 6 mois à 7 ans !\n\nLes enfants auront l'occasion d'explorer différents espaces d'éveil sensoriel et de jeux sensoriels conçus pour stimuler leur créativité, leur imagination, leurs apprentissages et leur plaisir de jouer. Nos séances sont libres et adaptées aux enfants, leur permettant d'explorer à leur propre rythme dans un environnement sûr et chaleureux.\n\nJouez, explorez, créez et amusez-vous !"},{"marketVariantId":"Spanish","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"SPAN-EUR","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Spanish","commentText":"¡Una aventura de juego sensorial y creativo en el histórico Rivermill con nuestro programa de actividades para niños de 6 meses a 7 años durante las vacaciones escolares!\n\nLos niños tendrán la oportunidad de explorar diversas estaciones de juego sensorial y creativo, diseñadas para fomentar la creatividad, la imaginación, el aprendizaje y el juego. Nuestras sesiones están dirigidas por los propios niños, permitiéndoles explorar a su ritmo en un entorno seguro y acogedor.\n\n¡Juega, explora, crea y ensúciate!"},{"marketVariantId":"Portuguese","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"PORT-EUR","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Portuguese","commentText":"Uma aventura divertida e cheia de atividades sensoriais no histórico Rivervmill, com nosso programa de férias escolares para crianças de 6 meses a 7 anos!\n\nAs crianças terão a oportunidade de explorar diversas estações sensoriais e de brincadeiras com tinta, projetadas para estimular a criatividade, a imaginação, o aprendizado e a diversão. Nossas sessões são conduzidas pelas crianças, permitindo que os pequenos explorem no seu próprio ritmo, em um ambiente seguro e acolhedor.\n\nBrinque, explore, crie e se suje!"},{"marketVariantId":"German","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"GERMAN","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"German","commentText":"Ein lustiges und kreatives Spielabenteuer in der historischen Rivermill erwartet Sie in unserem Ferienprogramm für Kinder von 6 Monaten bis 7 Jahren!\n\nDie Kinder können verschiedene Sinnes- und Spielstationen erkunden, die Kreativität, Fantasie, Lernen und freies Spielen fördern. Unsere Angebote sind kindgerecht gestaltet, sodass die Kleinen in einer sicheren und einladenden Umgebung in ihrem eigenen Tempo entdecken können.\n\nSpielen, entdecken, gestalten und nach Herzenslust matschen!"},{"marketVariantId":"Japanese","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"JAPANESE","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Japanese","commentText":"歴史あるリバーミルで、6ヶ月から7歳のお子様を対象とした、楽しい泥んこ遊びアドベンチャー！\n\nお子様は、創造性、想像力、学習、そして遊び心を育むためにデザインされた、様々な感覚刺激と泥んこ遊びのステーションを自由に探索できます。セッションは子ども主導で行われるため、小さなお子様は安全で温かい環境の中で、自分のペースで自由に探索できます。\n\n遊んで、探検して、創造して、思いっきり汚れて遊ぼう！"},{"marketVariantId":"Chinese Simplified","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"CHINESE-S","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Chinese Simplified","commentText":"在历史悠久的河畔磨坊，参加我们为6个月至7岁儿童举办的学校假期游戏活动，体验充满乐趣的涂鸦游戏之旅！\n\n孩子们将有机会探索各种感官游戏和涂鸦游戏区，这些游戏区旨在激发创造力、想象力、学习能力和玩耍热情。我们的活动以儿童为主导，让孩子们在安全友好的环境中按照自己的节奏探索。\n\n尽情玩耍、探索、创造，玩得不亦乐乎！"},{"marketVariantId":"Italian","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"ITALIAN","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Italian","commentText":"Un'avventura divertente e creativa allo storico Rivermill con il nostro programma di gioco per le vacanze scolastiche, dedicato ai bambini dai 6 mesi ai 7 anni!\n\nI bambini avranno l'opportunità di esplorare diverse postazioni sensoriali e di gioco creativo, pensate per stimolare la creatività, l'immaginazione, l'apprendimento e il divertimento. Le nostre sessioni sono guidate dai bambini, permettendo loro di esplorare al proprio ritmo in un ambiente sicuro e accogliente.\n\nGioca, esplora, crea e sporcati!"},{"marketVariantId":"Chinese Traditional","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"CHINESE-T","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Chinese Traditional","commentText":"在歷史悠久的河畔磨坊，參加我們為6個月至7歲兒童舉辦的學校假期遊戲活動，體驗充滿樂趣的塗鴉遊戲之旅！\n\n孩子們將有機會探索各種感官遊戲和塗鴉遊戲區，這些遊戲區旨在激發創造力、想像、學習能力和玩耍熱情。我們的活動以兒童為主導，讓孩子在安全友善的環境中以自己的步調探索。\n\n盡情玩樂、探索、創造，玩得不亦樂乎！"}],"productSite":[{"siteName":"Historic Rivermill","attributeIdSiteType":"VENUE","attributeIdSiteTypeDescription":"Venue","productSiteAddressRelationship":[{"attributeIdAddress":"PHYSICAL","attributeIdAddressDescription":"Physical","addressLine1":"950 Beaudesert Nerang Road","addressLine2":"","suburbName":"","cityName":"Mount Nathan","areaName":"","stateName":"Queensland","countryName":"Australia","addressPostalCode":"4211","overrideDomesticRegionFlag":"0","geocodeGdaLatitude":"-27.9760432","geocodeGdaLongitude":"153.2507233","productSiteAddressStreetDirectoryRelationship":""}],"productSiteAttributeRelationship":"","productSiteCommentRelationship":"","productSiteCommunicationRelationship":"","productSiteLicenceRelationship":"","productSiteRelatedSiteRelationship":"","productSiteMultimediaRelationship":"","productSiteContactRelationship":""}],"mediaLinks":[],"alternateNames":[],"internationalReach":"","rates":[{"ratesType":"ALLTICKETS","ratesTypeDescri