s super cute class! You'll be using both fondant and buttercream in this beginner class.\nClasses held in store at Cordies Cake Supplies"},{"marketVariantId":"Spanish","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"SPAN-EUR","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Spanish","commentText":"Clase para niños: Clase de cupcakes Lafufu.\n\n¡Niños a partir de 5 años son bienvenidos a esta adorable clase! En esta clase para principiantes, usarán fondant y crema de mantequilla.\n\nLas clases se imparten en la tienda Cordies Cake Supplies."},{"marketVariantId":"Indonesian","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"INDONESIAN","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Indonesian","commentText":"Kelas Anak-Anak: Kelas Cupcake Lafufu.\n\nAnak-anak berusia 5 tahun ke atas dipersilakan mengikuti kelas yang sangat lucu ini! Kalian akan menggunakan fondant dan buttercream di kelas pemula ini.\n\nKelas diadakan di toko Cordies Cake Supplies."},{"marketVariantId":"Japanese","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"JAPANESE","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Japanese","commentText":"キッズクラス：ラフフカップケーキ教室\n\n5歳以上のお子様が参加できる、とってもキュートなクラスです！初心者向けのこのクラスでは、フォンダンとバタークリームの両方を使います。\n\n教室はCordies Cake Suppliesの店舗で開催されます。"},{"marketVariantId":"French","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"FRENCH","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"French","commentText":"Atelier enfants : Atelier Cupcakes Lafufu.\n\nLes enfants dès 5 ans sont les bienvenus à cet atelier super mignon ! Vous utiliserez à la fois du fondant et de la crème au beurre lors de cet atelier d'initiation.\n\nAteliers dispensés en magasin chez Cordies Cake Supplies."},{"marketVariantId":"Portuguese","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"PORT-EUR","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Portuguese","commentText":"Aula para Crianças: Aula de Cupcakes Lafufu.\n\nCrianças a partir de 5 anos são bem-vindas nesta aula super fofa! Nesta aula para iniciantes, você usará pasta americana e buttercream.\n\nAulas realizadas na loja Cordies Cake Supplies."},{"marketVariantId":"Korean","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"KOREAN","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Korean","commentText":"어린이 강좌: 라푸푸 컵케이크 강좌\n\n5세 이상 어린이라면 누구나 참여할 수 있는 귀엽고 재미있는 컵케이크 강좌입니다! 초급반인 이 강좌에서는 폰단트와 버터크림을 모두 사용하게 됩니다.\n강좌는 코디스 케이크 용품 매장에서 진행됩니다."},{"marketVariantId":"Italian","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"ITALIAN","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Italian","commentText":"Corso per bambini: Lafufu Cupcakes.\n\nI bambini dai 5 anni in su sono i benvenuti in questo corso super carino! In questo corso per principianti userete sia la pasta di zucchero che la crema al burro.\nI corsi si tengono presso il negozio Cordies Cake Supplies."},{"marketVariantId":"German","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"GERMAN","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"German","commentText":"Kinderkurs: Lafufu Cupcakes-Kurs.\n\nKinder ab 5 Jahren sind in diesem superniedlichen Kurs herzlich willkommen! In diesem Anfängerkurs verwenden wir Fondant und Buttercreme. Der Kurs findet im Geschäft von Cordies Cake Supplies statt."},{"marketVariantId":"Chinese Simplified","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"CHINESE-S","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Chinese Simplified","commentText":"儿童课程：Lafufu 纸杯蛋糕课程。\n\n欢迎 5 岁及以上儿童参加这门超级可爱的课程！这门入门课程将使用翻糖和奶油霜。\n\n课程在 Cordies Cake Supplies 店内举办。"},{"marketVariantId":"Chinese Traditional","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"CHINESE-T","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Chinese Traditional","commentText":"兒童課程：Lafufu 紙杯蛋糕課程。\n\n歡迎 5 歲及以上兒童參加這門超可愛的課程！這門入門課程將使用翻糖和奶油霜。\n\n課程在 Cordies Cake Supplies 店內舉辦。"}],"productSite":[{"siteName":"Cordies Cake Supplies","attributeIdSiteType":"VENUE","attributeIdSiteTypeDescription":"Venue","productSiteAddressRelationship":[{"attributeIdAddress":"PHYSICAL","attributeIdAddressDescription":"Physical","addressLine1":"6 Dan Street","addressLine2":"1","suburbName":"","cityName":"Capalaba","areaName":"","stateName":"Queensland","countryName":"Australia","addressPostalCode":"4157","overrideDomesticRegionFlag":"0","geocodeGdaLatitude":"-27.5225823","geocodeGdaLongitude":"153.1987258","productSiteAddressStreetDirectoryRelationship":""}],"productSiteAttributeRelationship":"","productSiteCommentRelationship":"","productSiteCommunicationRelationship":"","productSiteLicenceRelationship":"","productSiteRelatedSiteRelationship":"","productSiteMultimediaRelationship":"","productSiteContactRelationship":""}],"mediaLinks":[],"alternateNames":[],"internationalReach":"","rates":[{"ratesType":"ALLTICKETS","ratesTypeDescription":"All tickets","priceFrom":"65","priceTo":"65","free":"","rateComment":"Price per person - all classes held in store at Cordies Cake Supplies - 1/6 Dan St Capalaba QLD 4